01468 inline byte
01469 ExpandRouteReplyPacket::createAttributes( bool freeway, bool ramp,
01470                                           bool driveOnRightSide )
01471 {
01472    // Bit 0 (LSB) : freeway
01473    // Bit 1       : ramp
01474    // Bit 2       : driveOnRightSide
01475    byte attributes = 0;
01476    if (freeway) {
01477       attributes |= 0x1;
01478    }
01479    
01480    if (ramp) {
01481       attributes |= 0x2;
01482    }
01483 
01484    if ( driveOnRightSide ) {
01485       attributes |= 0x4;
01486    }
01487    
01488    return (attributes);
01489 }
01490 
01491 inline void 
01492 ExpandRouteReplyPacket::extractAttributes( byte attributes, 
01493                                            bool& freeway,
01494                                            bool& ramp,
01495                                            bool& driveOnRightSide )
01496 {
01497    // Bit 0 (LSB) : freeway
01498    // Bit 1       : ramp
01499    // Bit 2       : driveOnRightSide
01500    if (attributes & 0x1) {
01501       freeway = true;
01502    } else {
01503       freeway = false;
01504    }
01505    
01506    if (attributes & 0x2) {
01507       ramp = true;
01508    } else {
01509       ramp = false;
01510    }
01511 
01512    if ( attributes & 0x4 ) {
01513       driveOnRightSide = true;
01514    } else {
01515       driveOnRightSide = false;
01516    }
01517 }
